body: Oddly, creating the guild doesn't automatically make you a member. HMs have to manually subscribe to their own guilds.

body:
Because +LeMemery is a private guild, the member count only includes approved contributors. [I think that this is confusing and should change](https://ruqqus.com/+BetaFeedback/post/68x3/the-subscriber-count-of-a-private).

<sup> - sfrohne [ If you're going to post a screenshot of this comment, **don't** censor my username | [RIP Klenny](https://ruqq.us/2g1v) | lslu ]</sup>
